flowchart TD
    Start([Read row: CIDR Subnet]) --> NmapSweep[Nmap Sweep: ICMP Ping + TCP 22]
    NmapSweep --> Filter[Filter Responding IPs into Array]
    Filter --> Loop[Loop through Responding IPs]
    Loop --> ProcessIP[Execute Sub-script: process_single_ip.py]
    ProcessIP --> NextIP{More IPs?}
    NextIP -->|Yes| ProcessIP
    NextIP -->|No| End([Subnet Processing Complete])
